folder: Westchester Avenue & Ward Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
Westchester Avenue,(foreground),north side, from Ward Avenue (right) to Boynton Avenue, showing part 1 of a panoramic view of the vast Watson estate during the time when the property was being leveled out for the construction of thoroughfares and parceled out for residential development. Several one-story brick buildings and an apartment house were later erected on this part of the
avenue.
About 1910

folder: Westchester Avenue & Ward Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
Westchester Avenue (foreground), north side, from Ward Avenue (right) to Boynton Avenue, showing part 1 of a panoramic view of the large Watson estate. The property is shown being leveled out for the construction of public thoroughfares and for future development. This is mount 1B and shows the same section of the estate as seen on mount
1A, taken several months later.
About 1910
